#: preparing.xml:672
#, no-c-format
msgid "The netmask to use with your network."
msgstr "Die Netzmaske zur Verwendung in Ihrem Netzwerk."

#. Tag: para
#: preparing.xml:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
