"Service) server."
msgstr ""
"Den Rechner in Ihrem Netzwerk, den Sie als DNS-(Domain Name Service-)Server "
"verwenden sollen."

#. Tag: para
#: preparing.xml:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the network you are connected to uses DHCP (Dynamic Host Configuration "
